snippet: Britain's Jamie Murray gained an early claim to bragging rights over younger brother Andy when he combined with Brazil's Bruno Soares to win the Australian Open men's doubles title early on Sunday....
lead_paragraph: Britain's Jamie Murray gained an early claim to bragging rights over younger brother Andy when he combined with Brazil's Bruno Soares to win the Australian Open men's doubles title early on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Murray (Senior) Wins First Australian Open Title
headline.main: Murray (Senior) Wins First Australian Open Title
